name: Oil Level Gauge
description: The Oil Level Gauge was developed in response to the need of maintenance professionals to gauge the oil level inside gearboxes.

name: Regulator
description: A quality regulator/rectifier that replaces the Suzuki AN 125 AN125 Burgman 95-00 OEM part. Works cooler and with more power as original rectifier.

name: Fuel Tank
description: The main function of the fuel tank is simply to hold fuel. However, it also provides a secure area for the knees to grip while riding, acting as an important point of contact between bike and rider.

name: Ignition Switch
description: An ignition switch, or starter switch, is the leading switch that administers the power in the main electrical of a motorcycle. In more simple terms, it's where your key goes to turn the bike on.

name: Main & Counter Shaft
description: A mechanism used to transmit motion and power from a main driving shaft to an individual machine, typically mounted by hangers on a ceiling, and driven by one belt from the main shaft.

name: Starting Clutch
description: The starter drive clutch is a one way roller clutch and a key component in a starter motor that is used to crank internal combustion engines.
